Package com.penthera.virtuososdk.client

Class QueueObserver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.penthera.virtuososdk.client.QueueObserver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observers.IObserver, Observers.IQueueObserver
    public class QueueObserver
extends Object
implements Observers.IQueueObserver
    Provides a base class implementation of the IQueueObserver interface, making private implementation of interface methods optional. The base implementation of each interface method does nothing.
